---
title: Gyro Lamb Patties with Yogurt Sauce and Quick Pickled Shallot
description: No need to fly to Greece or hit up your local Halal cart, we're making lamb gyros at home! This quick wrap comes together in a flash.
image: https://img.hellofresh.com/f_auto,fl_lossy,h_640,q_auto,w_1200/hellofresh_s3/image/galettes-d-agneau-style-gyros-e3cf5f95.jpg
